                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A spirit oni can be worn as a mask by a willing Small or Medium creature. While wearing the oni in this way, the wearer can see through the oni\u2019s eyes and speak through its mouth, although the wearer retains its own senses and voice. The oni grants its wearer a +2 insight bonus to Perception checks. The spirit oni remains a separate creature and must detach from the wearer\u2019s face (as a move action) if it wishes to take any action of its own (including attacking or using a spell-like ability).",
